data.text: Here comes the winds ahead of #HurricaneDorian2019. Outer band effects being felt here. Wind is strong. rain now moving in(after this video was taken). Bad hair days for everyone 😅😂 @FITSCAMS #Meteorology #weather #FLwx https://t.co/TBPrujt3uw
